To download any file from site
wget FILE NAME.tar.zg

UNZIP
tar vzxf drush-7.x-5.4.tar.gz
chmod u+x drush /*Make executable*/
ln -s /root/drush/drush /usr/bin/drush /*Make symlink*/

Check drush is working or not
go to root type 
drush or drush Help

drush status
drush dl MODULE NAME
drush en MODULE NAME 
drush cron

To rome any folder Command
rm -rf NAME oF FOLDER

To change the password for any user
drush upwd USERNAME --password="SOMEPASSWORD"

If you execute drush uli some-username, this will generate one time login link for that user.
drush uli some-username

